data.description:
Odaily Planet Daily News LBank released its second quarter 2025 operating report today, continuing its leading position in the Memecoin field and continuing to achieve outstanding results in asset growth and market share.
Assets: A total of 329 new currencies were launched this quarter, of which Meme accounted for 57%;
Growth: Multiple Meme projects achieved significant growth: LAUNCHCOIN increased by 15,194%, DUPE increased by 13,367%, and MIXIE increased by 6,742%;
Market share: LABUBU has become the most influential Memecoin project with a market share of 60.71%, strongly surpassing other centralized exchanges.
Memecoin transaction activity has increased:
The average daily transaction volume increased from 7.24% in the same period of 2024 to 12.98%;
The proportion of trading users to the overall platform users increased from 41.62% to 61.64%.
LBank continues to provide global Meme enthusiasts with first-hand spot, contract channels and ecological incubation support with advantages such as "fastest coin listing", "first liquidity" and "100% transaction compensation", and consolidates its leading position through core keywords such as "first in the world in 100-fold coin ratio", "first in the increase of first-issue assets" and "first in Meme market share CEX".
